  <title>Format of dates and time</title>
<p>You can change the format of the <gui>Date</gui> column by setting your preferred format under <guiseq><gui>Edit</gui><gui>Preferences</gui><gui>Mail Preferences</gui><gui>Headers</gui><gui>Date/Time format</gui></guiseq>.</p><p>The placeholders in the format expression are strftime variables.</p>
